headline: Rockwell Automation (NYSE:ROK): Strongest Q1 Results from the Internet of Things Group
summary: Quarterly earnings results are a good time to check in on a company’s progress, especially compared to its peers in the same sector. Today we are looking at Rockwell Automation (NYSE:ROK) and the best and worst performers in the internet of things industry.
